item.title: My work:"Updating"
item.dc:creator: @goatee goatee
item.description:
@goatee wrote:

Okay some CC:

1)5/10
Good - The text… goes well with the background but not the render. A nice background though.

Bad- Ewwww bad quality jpeg poop render. And if you screw up the border why not fix it before you post it? That just sorta confused me a bit.

2)4/10

Good- Background and text… try not to over use the font like you have in nearly every sig youveput here.

Bad- Dont everuse a cartoon render unless you adjust the brightness and contrast first… i never just “slap on” a render. Take your time with it and change the color of the outer glow. Does not blend well with the background, try changing opacity and press ctrl+U to change stuff… to change the color tick colorise.

  1. 5/10
    Good- Nice render… but obviously you didnt spend much time on that.

Bad- Boring background. Try grunge brushes or go to www.deviantart.com and search for metalCX … his brushes are amazing.

  1. 7/10
    Good- you have greatly improved and used a nice style for the background. Very original (I think).

Bad- Use a different font cos im getting bored! go to www.dafont.com for some great free fonts.

5)7/10
Hmmm…
Good- Your render fits well with the background. You have probably done somthing to the render to make it look like that… though I’m not sure what.

Bad- The font my love! Yet again you have usedit against me. Seeing as the render is a symbol of a retro gaming era i suggest you try gerting a retro font and manipulating it to your tastes. Incase you didnt know, using filters on a text layer can be very stupid. Before you try playing with the text, rasterize the layer by right clicking on it.

  1. 3/10
    Just… just no. Never do that agian! Bad boy bad boy!
  1. N.A/10

What excactly did you do to this signature… just lookslike you copied images and slapped some filters on. No matter what they say, simple is not always best!

  1. 8/10
    Good- Animation is great, even though you used a very easy technique it is very effective to the signature. The colors in the signature all mix well and you have improved loads with this peice.

Bad- The font… dont make me shout at you cos i will!
SHOUT!!!

  1. 2/10
    Sorry … just doesnt work… nothing much i can say about this.

The 9.5 one lol) 4/10

Good- Not much … dont know why you posted this really.

Bad- All the same bland color.

  1. 8/10

Good- The background is great… and so is the render… colors fit together perfectly and i really like this.

Bad- Ummm nothing really… Maybe add a border to this piece?

  1. 6/10
    Good- The background is good… too bad it clashes with the render.

Bad- Eww ewww icky render… ever played with blend modes? Try it, it’s fun!

  1. 9.5/10
    Good- Nice renders, crisp and works weith the colorsw in the piece, even the text goes well with it all. Really nice stuff you got there

Bad- Bit of a grainy background, and whats up with the strange bit under the “M”?

[center]---------------[/center]

Good work solemage… just please use a different font lol!
That took me fucking ages to write.

Read full topic
